
nnoremap <TAB> :bnext<CR>       " TAB in general mode will move to text buffer
nnoremap <S-TAB> :bprevious<CR> " SHIFT-TAB will go back

" Better window navigation
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

nnoremap <Leader>o o<Esc>^Da
nnoremap <Leader>O O<Esc>^Da

" Better tabbing
vnoremap < <gv
vnoremap > >gv
